{"tid":241604,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「做下宣傳」西洋書法嘅心得分享","createTime":"2017-05-13T09:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T02:42:34.000Z","uid":23863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a065dd198b126fa0627db3eb95457ca1da4af93e","tid":241604,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"又係我哋Happy Kongner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今日我哋出咗一條關於西洋書法嘅片。<br />\n我諗作為香港人，細過讀書果陣都會做過CopyBook 之類嘅功課，為嘅就係寫到一手簡潔又易明嘅英文字啦，但大家又知唔知究竟咩叫做西洋書法呢？我哋就請咗一位西洋書法愛好者，同大家下究竟西洋書法係啲乜嚟。<br />\n如果大家對西洋書法有興趣或者想了解多啲嘅話，就千祈唔好錯過我哋以下呢條片啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6PIQon2M6jo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6PIQon2M6jo&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=20553a91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6PIQon2M6jo</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲睇完覺得幾好嘅，不妨比個Like 或者Subscribe 我哋呢個Channel 啦，因為你哋嘅支持先至係我哋創作最大嘅原動力。<br />\n而如果睇完有咩問題又或者有啲咩想講，都可以去我哋條片下面留個言，又或者去我哋嘅Facebook Page 討論一下。<br />\n呢個係我哋嘅Facebook Page:<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/happykongner/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhappykongner%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6e045dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/happykongner/</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持香港文化！"},{"pid":"7c771fb0d5ce3fd29af97734a59b43e51bf26edc","tid":241604,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"好似幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250e8541e4a9b46f3d47dac2da3317a51ec9ef3d","tid":241604,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"星期六學術台冇人"},{"pid":"0e20b92cf744416c57cdaa6b25bc500103884f7d","tid":241604,"uid